name: Wedding Dress Extension | Clothing LoRA
description:
MAJOR UPDATE

  • WeddingDressEXv0.4 [Reduce the fit of the model and improve the diversity]

  • WeddingDressEX_Champagne [A relatively fixed category of champagne wedding dresses for special purposes]

Yes, there will be a WEDDING DRESS in every Real person model.

In this LoRA, I enhanced certain FEATURE recognition of wedding dresses.

沒錯，每個真人向模型都包含婚紗，在這個LoRA中我對婚紗的特性進行了強調，使表達更精確！

Style features

  • "tulle"

  • "suspender"

  • "off-shoulder"

  • "with a V-neckline"

  • "huge skirt" (generic)

  • "long tail" (low impact)

  • "black wedding dress" (low impact)

  • "with a long sleeve"

Lace pattern

  • "heavy lace"

  • "with willow-shaped lace"

  • "with flower-shaped lace"

Other decoration

  • "studded with sparkling gemstone"

  • "with pearl embellishments"

Pose

  • "front view"

  • "back view + with her back to the viewer" (great effect!!!)

Parameter

Using ChilloutMix, with same prompt and parameter except weddingdressEX. (WeddingDressEXv0.2)

More

歡迎朋友們加我微信交流：artist3yehe

Reach me on Twitter if you wish to contribute to improving this mod, Thx! https://twitter.com/Artist3YeHe
